  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个请求流转的时序图，从外部用户到最终服务。首先，Client 发起 HTTPS GET 请求到 LoadBalancer，然后 LoadBalancer 再转发给 NGINX。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Client",
        "LoadBalancer",
        "NGINX",
        "HTTPS GET /"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，LoadBalancer 到 NGINX 这一段是用 HTTP 还是 HTTPS？另外，NGINX 后面直接连到 Webservice 吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "LoadBalancer",
        "NGINX",
        "Webservice"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "LoadBalancer 到 NGINX 可以是 HTTP 或 HTTPS，你标注成 HTTP(S) 吧。对，NGINX 后面要加一个路由判断的 loop，根据 Host 或 ServerAlias 来决定怎么转发，然后再发到 Webservice。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "LoadBalancer",
        "NGINX",
        "Webservice",
        "loop route",
        "Host/ServerAlias"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我加上 loop 块，NGINX 内部做 route 判断，然后 NGINX 发 HTTP GET 到 Webservice。返回数据我用虚线箭头往回画。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "NGINX",
        "Webservice",
        "loop route",
        "HTTP GET /"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "返回的状态码要体现两种情况：302 重定向或者 200 正常返回，content 也要带回去。路径是 Webservice → NGINX → LoadBalancer → Client，逐级返回。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Webservice",
        "NGINX",
        "LoadBalancer",
        "Client",
        "HTTP 302/200",
        "content"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下，所有返回都是虚线箭头对吧？而且每一层都要把 content 传回去，Client 最终拿到的是 LoadBalancer 返回的 302 或 200。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Webservice",
        "NGINX",
        "LoadBalancer",
        "Client",
        "content",
        "HTTP 302/200"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，就是这样。激活状态也注意一下，Client、LoadBalancer、NGINX 和 Webservice 在交互期间都要保持激活。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Client",
